ote_> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\">AP</title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">5.176</biblScope> </bibl> </cit> (<bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Mel.\">Mel.</a></author> </bibl>); <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">σιμὰ σεσηρὼς μυχθίζεις</foreign> ib.<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg1492.tlg001:178\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">178</biblScope> </bibl> (Id.); cf. <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">σιμόω</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg1492.tlg001:1\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1</biblScope></bibl></cit>. </sense> <sense n=\"II\" id=\"n94185.2\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> metaph., <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">bent upwards</tr_>, <abbr TEIform=\"abbr\">like</abbr> the slope of a hillside: hence, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">up-hill</tr_>, opp. <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">κατάντης, χωρίον</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0019.tlg007.perseus-grc1:288\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ar.\">Ar.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Lys.\">Lys.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">288</biblScope></bibl></cit>, ubi <abbr TEIform=\"abbr\">v.</abbr> Sch.; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">πρὸς τὸ ς. διώκειν</foreign> pursue <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">up-hill</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0032.tlg001.perseus-grc1:4:3:23\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ X.\">X.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ HG\">HG</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4.3.23</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">πρὸς τὸ ς. ἀνατρέχειν</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0445.tlg001:4\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Dionys.Com.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf.<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0086.tlg036:870a:30\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Arist.\">Arist.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pr.\">Pr.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">870a30</biblScope> </bibl>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ς. [ὁδός]</foreign> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0032.tlg014.perseus-grc1:6:5\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ X.\">X.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Cyn.\">Cyn.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">6.5</biblScope> </bibl>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ὑπερβάλλειν τὰ ς</foreign>. ib.<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0032.tlg014.perseus-grc1:5:16\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">5.16</biblScope> </bibl>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">σίμαι</foreign> (sic cod.) the <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">ends</tr_> of the lyre, <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hsch.\">Hsch.</a></author> </bibl>; also, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">parts of the cornice</tr_>, Id., cf. <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Vitr.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3.5.12</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"2\" id=\"n94185.3\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> generally, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">hollow, concave</tr_>, opp. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">κυρτός, ἡ γαστὴρ τῶν ἀδείπνων ς</foreign>. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0032.tlg007.perseus-grc1:8:4:21\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ X.\">X.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Cyr.\">